(91, 55, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<p>A good place to start is by collecting basic facts and figures that will:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Identify what is already known about people with disabilities and the situation in which they live\n</li>\n<li>Provide baseline information that may be helpful for evaluation in the future\n</li>\n</ul>\n<i>Complete the following form to collect facts and figures about the environmental, social, economic, cultural and political situation at the national, regional and/or local level. Select <strong>Save</strong> when you are finished.</i>\n<p>Collect all of the data you can find related to the following topics. Collecting this information may involve:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Talking to people</li>\n<li>Visiting local government offices</li>\n<li>Reviewing documents and data that can be found:\n<ul>\n<li>On the Internet</li>\n<li>In government publications</li>\n<li>In books and research papers</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Topic</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">In local communities</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>At the regional level</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>At the national level</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>Population</i></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Total number of people with disabilities</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow rbackgroundtable\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Number of males with disabilities </div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment4\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Number of females with disabilities</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment7\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment8\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment9\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Average age of people with disabilities</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment10\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment11\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment12\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow rbackgroundtable\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Number with visual impairments</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment13\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment14\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment15\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Number with hearing impairments</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment16\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment17\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment18\'></textarea><br/></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableR