(225, 57, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<p>It is important to identify all key stakeholders and involve them from the beginning of the management cycle to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ensure their participation\n</li>\n<li>Help establish a sense of community ownership\n</li>\n<li>Increase programme sustainability\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>A stakeholder analysis helps to identify those stakeholders (individuals, groups or organizations) that might benefit from, contribute to, or influence a CBR programme.\n</p>\n<p><i>Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>Identify stakeholders</b></p>\n<p>Begin by identifying all key stakeholders, assessing the strengths and weaknesses of each, and making a preliminary determination of what roles and responsibilities each stakeholder could assume in your organisation.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Stakeholder</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Current level of interest in disability\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Current level of influence\n</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Strengths (resources, knowledge, skills, etc.)\n</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Weaknesses</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Potential roles and responsibilities</strong></div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">People with disabilities and their families</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">  Play an active role in all parts of managing a CBR programme<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Participate in local CBR committees<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Volunteer and/or work as CBR personnel<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Work to increase awareness about disability<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Community members</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">  Participate in training opportunities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Change their beliefs and attitudes<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\"> Address other barriers to accessibility<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Include people with disabilities in activitie<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  Contribute resources (e.g. time, money, equipment)<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\"> Address the causes of disability<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\"> Provide support and assistance to people with disabilities where needed<br>\n\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Civil society</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">Develop and implement CBR programmes where there is limited government support<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide technical assistance, resources and training<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Support the development of referral networks between stakeholders<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Support CBR programmes to build the capacity of other stakeholders<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Mainstream disability into existing programmes and services<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Support the evaluation, research and development of CBR<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Disabled people’s organizations</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">Represent the interests of people with disabilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide advice about the needs of people with disabilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Educate people with disabilities about their rights<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Advocate and lobby for action to ensure that governments and service providers are responsive to these rights<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide information about services to people with disabilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Directly manage CBR programmes<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Local government</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">Implement and manage a national CBR programme<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Put in place all necessary legislation and policies to support the rights of people with disabilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Develop a national CBR policy<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide human, material, and financial resources for CBR programmes<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Ensure that people with disabilities are able to access all public services and facilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Develop CBR as an operational methodology or service delivery mechanism<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">CBR staff members</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">Identify people with disabilities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Carry out basic assessments of their function<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide simple therapeutic interventions<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Educate family members<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Provide information about available services, and link people with disabilities with these services<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Assist in the formation of self-help groups<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Advocate for improved accessibility and inclusion<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Raise awareness in the community about disability<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">CBR managers</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"Bike\">Facilitate each stage of the management cycle<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Manage day-to-day activities through delegation<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Mobilize and manage financial, human and material resources<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Support and supervise CBR staff members<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Put in place all necessary policies, systems and procedures<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Build and maintain networks and partnerships<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Involve all key stakeholders in each stage of the management cycle<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Build the capacity of communities<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Coordinate with organizations doing similar work to avoid duplication of effort<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Ensure that disability issues are mainstreamed into the development sector<br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">Manage information systems to monitor progress and performance<br>\n\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment5\'></textarea><br/><br>\n<input type=\"checkbox\"  value=\"roles\">  <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment6\'></textarea><br/><br>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">other <textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\n<d