(347, 65, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<p>All communities have resources, even those that are very poor. The purpose of a resource analysis is to identify the resources currently available in a community that a CBR programme could use or build on.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to perform a resource analysis. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>Human resources</b></p>\n<p>Begin by identifying individuals in the local community who have the motivation, talent, skills and/or influence to provide valuable support to CBR. Be sure to evaluate the capacity (i.e. the strengths and weaknesses) of each individual to address the needs of people with disabilities.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name of individual</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Position (or Title)</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Strengths</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Weaknesses</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-11 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-12 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-13 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-14 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-15 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-16 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-17 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-18 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[textarea textarea-19 rows:2 cols:20]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell 