(538, 76, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<p>Although the resources that are needed for a CBR programme may not be immediately available when the programme starts, it is important to think about the resources needed to implement the programme activities and how to go about obtaining them.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to start the resource-planning process for your organization. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><i>List the different types of resources that your programme will require in the tables below. Then indicate how it may be possible to obtain each one:</i></p>\n<ul>\n<li>From mainstream organizations\n</li>\n<li>From the local government\n</li>\n<li>From donors or volunteers\n</li>\n<li>Through programme funding\n</li>\n<li>From local businesses\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>It is important to consider the long-term sustainability of the programme when specifying what resources will be required. It is also important to make sure that all budgeted expenses are inclusive of the actual costs needed to work with people with disabilities.</p>\n<p>Remember to refer back to the Resource analysis to identify the resources that already exist.</p>\n<p><b>Human resources</b></p>\n<p>List the types of personnel needed to implement the programme, and how these positions might be obtained:</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Mainstream <br> organizations</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Local <br> government</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Donors or <br> volunteers</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Programme <br> funding</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Local <br> businesses</b></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Programme manager</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-889 id:checkbox1 