(704, 91, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h3>Carry out planned activities</h3>\n<p>The second step involves making a decision about the best way to answer the evaluation questions, thinking about the following issues:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who can provide the information?</li>\n<li>How can the information be collected?</li>\n<li>When should it be collected?</li>\n</ul>\n<p><i>Complete this form to plan how and when to collect information. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>Who can provide the information?</b></p>\n<p>Select who can provide the information you need:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n People with disabilities and their families\"]<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Other stakeholders\"]<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n CBR personnel\"]<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Other community programmes\"]<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Government authorities\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Examples:</b> National statistics office\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>How can information be collected?</b></p>\n<p>Next, identify how the information will be collected. (Usually more than one method is used to collect information for an evaluation.)</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Expense records\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to:</p>\n<ul><li>Determine whether resources have been used as originally planned\n</li>\n<li>Provide assurance to funders that the programme is transparent and accountable\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Questionnaires\"]\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nIndividual assessments\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to assess individuals’ current state of well-being, health, daily activities, etc.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nSurveys\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to assess attitudinal changes and quality-of-life changes (especially when compared with baseline data)\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Documentation reviews\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can help to understand:</p>\n<ul><li>The policies underlying the programme</li>\n<li>How the programme operates</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nRecord reviews\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can provide an overview of:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The number and characteristics of clients</li>\n<li>The progress made</li>\n<li>The interventions made</li>\n<li>The relationship between inputs and results</li>\n<li>The workload of the rehabilitation workers</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Interviews\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can help to:</p>\n<ul><li>Understand an individual’s views, impressions or experiences</li>\n<li>Learn more about individuals’ answers to questionnaires</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Observation\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to gather accurate information about how a programme actually operates, particularly about processes and interactions\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Focus groups\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to explore a topic in depth through group discussion – for example:<br>\n<ul>\n<li>To learn about reactions to an experience or suggestion</li>\n<li>To reach a common understanding of problems and issues</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Public meetings\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to:\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Gather information from a wide range of sources</li>\n<li>Break down the distance between all citizens</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>When should information be collected?</b></p>\n<p>Information can be collected at different stages.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n Before a programme starts\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Provides baseline data that can be used to measure the impact a CBR programme has had.<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\n While the programme is underway\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to make adjustments to activities and processes.<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\nAt the end of the programme\"]\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>When compared with baseline data, indicates the impact the programme has had.<br>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
