(849, 101, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<p><b>Support health promotion campaigns</b></p>\n<p>Health promotion campaigns can positively influence the health of individuals, communities and populations – they can inform, encourage and motivate behaviour change. CBR should make a special effort to support existing health promotion efforts, and support the development of new campaigns when they are needed.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>1. Identify and contact existing health promotion campaigns</b></p>\n<p>Identify existing health promotion campaigns at the community, regional and national levels:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Campaign Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text1 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text2 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text4 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text5 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text6 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox size:10]<br/></div>\n\n</div>\n