ckbox \"Ask them what assistance they may need to achieve these goals\"]\n<p><b>2. Identify and contact communication resources in your community</b></p>\n<p>Identify resources in your community, such as community spokespersons, newspapers, radio, television and web sites, from whom community members regularly receive information.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Disability-Related Health Issue</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Potential Partner(s)</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text28 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \">[text text-248 id:text29 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
