(983, 107, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Promote clean water and sanitation</b></h5>\n<p>Water and sanitation measures contribute to improving healthy living and minimizing disability.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Provide training to ensure that CBR personnel are able to perform the following tasks:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-1 \"Talk to people with disabilities and their family members about the barriers they face when accessing and using water and sanitation facilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Examples:</b> People with disabilities may be unable to access water sources because:</p> \n<ul>\n<li>They live too far away</li>\n<li>The terrain is too rough</li>\n<li>The method for obtaining water from the wells is too difficult</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-107-2 class:checkbox \"Make local authorities and water and sanitation organizations aware of these barriers\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-3 \"Provide suggestions and ideas for ways to overcome the barriers in partnership with people with disabilities and their family members\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Install raised toilet seats and handrails to provide support for people unable to use a squat latrine</p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-107-4 class:checkbox \"Lobby and work with local authorities to adapt existing facilities and/or build new facilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-5 \"Encourage community members to support and assist people with disabilities where needed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Encourage neighbours to accompany a person with a disability when fetching water</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
