ext pn-r9 id:cf-122-33 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ia-r9 id:cf-122-34 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text l-r9 id:cf-122-35 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ci-r9 id:cf-122-36 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text pn-r10 id:cf-122-37 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ia-r10 id:cf-122-38 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text l-r10 id:cf-122-39 class:text size:25]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ci-r10 id:cf-122-40 class:text size:25]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Contact and work with the programmes</b></p>\n<p>Contact each of the programmes listed above and work with them to ensure that they are able to include people with disabilities and their families in their services. Work with each programme to ensure that:</p>\n[checkbox cb-pwd-41 id:cf-122-41 class:checkbox \"People with disabilities and their families are aware of the types of prevention activities the programme can offer\"]\n[checkbox cb-hp-42 id:cf-122-42 class:checkbox\"Health personnel are aware of the needs of people with disabilities\"]\n[checkbox cb-iap-43 id:cf-122-43 class:checkbox \"Information about prevention is available in appropriate formats\"]\n[checkbox cb-paa-44 id:cf-122-44 class:checkbox \"Prevention activities are available in locations close to where people live\"]\n[checkbox cb-tlw-44 id:cf-122-45 class:checkbox \"The locations where prevention activities take place are physically accessible (if not, provide practical ideas and solutions on ways to make them accessible)\"]\n[checkbox cb-psc-44 id:cf-122-46 class:checkbox \"Prevention services can be provided in alternative locations, such as in home environments, when access is difficult\"]\n</div>\n[hidden user default:user_id]\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>'),
