(1071, 113, '_form', '<h5>Become a health-promoting organization</h5>\n<p>Health promotion within workplaces has the capacity to improve staff morale and skills, job performance and, ultimately, health.</p>\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p>Does your organization:</p>\n<p><b>1. Provide a safe and healthy environment, including:</b></p>\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox101 class:checkbox \"A non-smoking environment\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox102 class:checkbox \"Safe water\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox103 class:checkbox \"Sanitary facilities\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox104 class:checkbox \"Reasonable working hours\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox105 class:checkbox \"Safe transport options\"]\n\n\n<p><b>2. Develop policies and practices within the organization which promote health, including policies against:</b></p>\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox106 class:checkbox \"Discrimination\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox107 class:checkbox \"Prejudice and stigma\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox108 class:checkbox \"Harassment\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox109 class:checkbox \"Tobacco, drug and alcohol use\"]\n\n\n<p><b>3. Other</b></p>\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox110 class:checkbox \"Provide training and education to all staff (regardless of the level at which they work) on ways to improve and maintain their health\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-242 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Encourage staff to be good role models in their communities, such as by setting good examples for others through their lifestyle choices.\"]\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>'),
