(1230, 136, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Help to prevent secondary conditions</b></h5>\n<p>People of all ages with disabilities are at risk of secondary conditions. CBR should promote primary prevention strategies to reduce the likelihood that people with disabilities will develop these conditions.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>To prevent secondary conditions, make sure CBR personnel are properly trained to perform the following tasks:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-1 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their family members are aware and knowledgeable about the secondary conditions commonly associated with their disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Examples:</b>  People with spinal cord injuries or spina bifida should be aware that they are at a high risk of developing urinary tract infections.</p> \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-134-5 \"Assist people with disabilities and their families to identify strategies that will help prevent secondary conditions from developing\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b>\n  <ul>\n<li>Adopt healthy lifestyle behaviours (e.g. exercise and good nutrition)\n</li>\n<li>Have regular health check-ups</li>\n<li>Maintain good hygiene</li>\n<li>Join self-help groups</li>\n</ul></p></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-134-6 class:checkbox \"Ensure that any assistive devices provided to people with disabilities do not create risks for secondary conditions\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Example:</b> Ensure that prostheses fit properly and do not cause red marks that can lead to pressure sores.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>');
