(1289, 140, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Assist with early identification</b></h5>\n<p>Early identification of a medical condition provides the best opportunity for curing or managing it. CBR personnel members who work directly in the community are often in a position to notice the early signs of a condition, and to provide the appropriate medical referral.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>CBR should work with primary health-care personnel to establish a mechanism for the early identification of health conditions and impairments associated with disability.</p>\n<p><b>Diseases</b></p>\n<p>CBR personnel can identify screening activities aimed at the early identification of common communicable or non-communicable diseases, and provide referrals as needed.</p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Disease</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Early signs or symptoms\n</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information for screening services\n</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Tuberculosis</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-1 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-2 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Leprosy</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-3 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-4 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Diabetes</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-5 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-6 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Cancer</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-7 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-8 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Filariasis</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-9 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-10 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">River blindness</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-11 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-12 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-13 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-14 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-15 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-16 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-17 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-18 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-19 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-20 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-21 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Provide information to people with disabilities and their families about the timing and location of the screening activities listed above, and ensure they are able to access these.</p>\n<p><b>Genetic or hereditary conditions</b></p>\n<p>CBR personnel should take steps to ensure that members of families with a history of genetic or hereditary conditions are referred to appropriate medical facilities for assessment and counselling.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Condition</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>Contact information for assessment/counseling services\n</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Muscular dystrophy</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-22 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-23 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-24 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-25 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-26 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-27 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-592 id:cf-140-28 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-994 id:cf-140-29 \"Identify people with impairments in the community who may benefit from surgery, and provide the appropriate referrals\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell  p-2  vertical\">Surgery can:<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Prevent impairments from becoming worse</li>\n<li>Contribute to improved functioning</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell  p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-0 id:cf-140-35 class:checkbox \"Be aware of secondary conditions and check for these when working with people with disabilities\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Example:</b> Pressure sores that are associated with certain disabilities</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
