(1408, 154, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Promote self-management of chronic conditions</b></h5>\n<p>CBR can assist people with disabilities and their families to become aware of their right to medical care and to learn skills that enable them to manage their chronic health conditions.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>To help people with chronic disabilities effectively manage their conditions themselves:</p>\n<p><b>Provide direct support</b></p>\n<p>Work directly with people with disabilities to:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage them to take responsibility for their own health by seeking appropriate medical care and making healthy lifestyle choices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Ensure that they are able to understand and follow medical advice\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Link people with disabilities to self-help groups to enable them to learn about self-management by sharing knowledge and skills with others\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Self-help group members can share ideas and experiences around:\n<ul>\n<li>What resources are available for medical care</li>\n<li>How to effectively negotiate the health-care system</li>\n<li>How to manage existing health conditions</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Provide direct support</b></p>\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Develop or adapt existing materials and publications that provide medical information about health conditions into formats that are appropriate for people with disabilities and their family members\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Be sure to:\n<ul>\n<li>Use simple language</li>\n<li>Use simple sketches or pictures</li>\n<li>Translate material into local languages</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
