(1460, 158, '_form', '<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Build relationships with medical-care providers</b></h5>\n<p>Medical personnel often have limited knowledge about disability and how best to enable access for people with disabilities to medical-care services. By making contact with medical services and building relationships with staff, CBR can develop a network that can be used to facilitate referrals and comprehensive medical care for people with disabilities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p><b>Communicate directly with medical personnel</b></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Promote awareness among medical personnel about the health needs of people with disabilities and their families\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Encourage medical personnel to involve people with disabilities and their family members in the development of medical treatment and care plans\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Work jointly with community health programmes to ensure that people with disabilities can access the benefits of these programmes\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Facilitate communication between medical personnel and others</b></p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Organize interactive sessions between individuals and groups of people with disabilities, family members and medical personnel to enable discussion of key issues related to disability and sharing of experiences\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Example topic</b>: Access issues</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Request that medical services provide education and training for CBR personnel\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Suggested topics</b>: How to:\n<ul>\n<li>Assist with early detection</li>\n<li>Provide referrals to appropriate services and</li>\n<li>Provide follow-up in the community</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),
