(55, 1, '2019-04-25 11:12:03', '2019-04-25 11:12:03', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p>A good place to start is by collecting basic facts and figures that will:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Identify what is already known about people with disabilities and the situation in which they live\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Provide baseline information that may be helpful for evaluation in the future\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<i>Complete the following form to collect facts and figures about the environmental, social, economic, cultural and political situation at the national, regional and/or local level. Select <strong>Save</strong> when you are finished.</i>\r\n<p>Collect all of the data you can find related to the following topics. Collecting this information may involve:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Talking to people</li>\r\n<li>Visiting local government offices</li>\r\n<li>Reviewing documents and data that can be found:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>On the Internet</li>\r\n<li>In government publications</li>\r\n<li>In books and research papers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Topic</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">In local communities</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>At the regional level</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>At the national level</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>Population</i></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell rbackgroundheader\"><i>&nbsp;</i></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">Total number of people with disabilities</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><textarea name=\'comment\' i