(69, 1, '2019-04-30 12:33:50', '2019-04-30 12:33:50', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p>It is likely that many different needs will have been identified which could all potentially be addressed by a CBR programme. Unfortunately, resources are not unlimited, and therefore priorities will need to be set. It is important that people with disabilities and other key stakeholders actively participate in the priority-setting process to ensure that the programme will be relevant and appropriate to their needs.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to start the priority-setting process for your organization. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Evaluate strengths and weaknesses</b></p>\r\n<p>Perform a SWOT analysis of your organization’s strengths and weaknesses and use this to identify a list of possible actions (which should be recorded below, in the second part of this form).</p>\r\n<p>During the SWOT analysis, brainstorm how to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Use strengths with opportunities to initiate positive changes\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Use strengths to reduce the impact of threats\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Use opportunities to mobilize resources and minimize weaknesses\r\n</li>\r\n<li>UControl damage when weaknesses and threats come together\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>&nbsp</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Helpful</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Harmful</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Internal</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><b>S</b>trengths:<br>[textarea textarea-188 id:textarea3 cols:50 rows:5]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><b>W</b>eaknesses<br>[textarea textarea-189 id:textarea3 cols:50 rows:5]<br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">External</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><b>O</b>pportunities:<br>[textarea textarea-190 id:textarea3 cols:50 rows:5]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><b>T</b>hreats:<br>[textarea textarea-191 id:textarea3 cols:50 rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>List and evaluate possible actions</b></p>\r\n<p>Record possible actions your organization might take in the table below. When you are finished, evaluate the actions by selecting <b>three</b> checkboxes in each of the remaining columns.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Possible action</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Which actions have the greatest potential for positive change?</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Which ones are most important to people with disabilities?</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Which ones best align with the Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities (CRPD)?</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Which ones are most feasible (i.e. the resources needed are available right now)?</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Which ones are most urgent (i.e. where is the need greatest)?</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical cols:15 rows:2\">[textarea textarea-158]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-125 use_label_element]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Representatives from as many stakeholder groups as possible should be invited to participate in the forum.</p>\r\n<p><i>Use the following form to plan your stakeholder forum(s)