(72, 1, '2019-05-02 05:16:14', '2019-05-02 05:16:14', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p>Preparing a programme plan is a critical step. Your programme plan should answer the following questions:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>What does your programme want to achieve? (goal and purpose)\r\n</li>\r\n<li>How will the programme achieve this? (outcomes, activities and resources)\r\n</li>\r\n<li>How will we know when the programme has achieved this? (indicators)\r\n</li>\r\n<li>How can we confirm that the programme has achieved this? (means of verification)\r\n</li>\r\n<li>What are the potential problems that may be experienced along the way? (risks)\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A logical framework (“log frame”) is a particularly useful tool in this planning exercise.</p>\r\n<p><i>Below are log frames for a number of the most important CBR components. Complete a form for each of the components that your programme plans to implement. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><b>Log frame for the Health component</b></p>\r\n <div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Summary</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Indicators</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Sources of verification</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Assumptions</strong></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Goal</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical \"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment1\'></textarea><br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment2\'></textarea><br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment3\'></textarea><br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><textarea name=\'comment\' id=\'comment4\'></textarea><br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\