(87, 1, '2019-05-06 08:48:45', '2019-05-06 08:48:45', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h3>Monitor programme activities</h3>\r\n<p>Monitoring involves the regular collection and analysis of information of programme activities. The monitoring process helps the CBR team identify which activities are going well and which are not, so that the necessary changes can be made. When good monitoring systems are in place and are effective, evaluation of the programme becomes much easier.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following checklist as a first step in planning your monitoring process. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p>The following steps are involved in monitoring a programme:</p>\r\n<p><b>1. Set indicators</b></p>\r\n<p>The indicators were defined earlier, during the <b>Planning and design</b> stage.</p>\r\n<p><b>2. Decide how to collect information</b></p>\r\n<p>The methods for collecting monitoring data were defined earlier, in the <b>Programme plan.</b></p>\r\n<p><b>3. Collect and record information:</b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Put in place formal systems for collecting and recording information\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Data collection systems should:<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Be as simple as possible</li>\r\n<li>Collect only the information that is required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nInstitute a regular data collection schedule\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Depending on the needs of your programme, schedules may be:<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Daily</li>\r\n<li>Weekly</li>\r\n<li>Monthly, and/or</li>\r\n<li>Quarterly</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nTrain all staff members in the use of these systems\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>4. Analyze information</b></p>\r\n<p>Collecting and recording information is often much easier than analyzing it. However, if CBR programme managers do not look closely at the information, they will not be able to observe the progress of the programme activities and identify any potential problems.</p><br>\r\n<p>To conduct an effective analysis, you will need to:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Summarize the data\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>This may require aggregating data from multiple sources<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Identify trends in the data\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Recognize what the trends suggest\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Discuss the findings with key stakeholders\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><b>5. Report and share information:</b></p>\r\n<p>Reporting and sharing the results of monitoring with key stakeholders shows that the programme is transparent and accountable. A monitoring report should include information on:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"The activity or work area being reported on\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Work planned for the period vs. work completed\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Progress towards the programme outcomes\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Budgeted vs. actual expenditures\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \" Achievements\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Constraints/problems\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Actions taken or recommended\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Lessons learnt\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Reporting requirements will vary depending on the management structures in place for CBR programmes. For example, at the local level, CBR personnel may need to report to the programme manager on a weekly basis, while programme managers may need to report to higher levels on a monthly basis, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><b>6. Manage the information</b></p>\r\n<p>A CBR programme can generate a lot of information (e.g. documents, reports, correspondence and written accounts). You will need to develop an effective system for managing all of this information.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Create an efficient filing system\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Having an efficient system will save a great deal of time and prevent misunderstandings during monitoring<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Store any confidential information being collected in a secure location\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Train all CBR staff in the proper procedures to follow when handling confidential information\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Locking storage cabinets and office doors</li>\r\n<li>Using strong passwords and encryption to protect data stored on computers</li>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Monitor programme activities', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'monitor-programme-activities', '', '', '2019-05-06 09:47:38', '2019-05-06 09:47:38', '', 0, 'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=87', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
