(98, 1, '2019-05-07 09:21:07', '2019-05-07 09:21:07', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h3>Share findings and take action</h3>\r\n<p>An evaluation is useless if no one acts on its conclusions and recommendations. It is therefore important to report on and share the evaluation findings.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form as a first step in planning how you will share your research findings. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Share findings</b></p>\r\n<p>Share your evaluation results and conclusions in one or more of the following ways:\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Conduct a meeting\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Meeting attendees could include:</p>\r\n<p>Different types of information are analyzed in different ways. For example:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul><li>People with disabilities</li>\r\n<li>Disabled people’s organizations</li>\r\n<li>Concerned stakeholders and community members</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Write a formal evaluation report\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Write an article for the local newspaper or professional journal\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Newspapers or journals to consider:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Present a paper at a conference\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Conferences to consider:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Take action</b></p>\r\n<p>After an evaluation, it is also important to reflect and learn from the things that worked and the things that did not.</p>\r\n<p>Use the evaluation results to make decisions about:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which aspects of the programme should continue\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which aspects need to be changed\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which aspects should be stopped\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which successful practices could be scaled up\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13\"\r\n Which other areas and priorities in the community need to be addressed\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Aspects to continue:</p>\r\n<p>[textarea textarea-403 id:textarea1 class:textarea]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox