(108, 1, '2019-05-08 09:14:08', '2019-05-08 09:14:08', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Educate health-care providers</b></p>\r\n<p>Health-care providers are a trusted source of health-related information and have the potential to positively influence the health of others. CBR needs to work with these providers to ensure they have adequate knowledge about disability and include people with disabilities in all their health promotion activities.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify health-care organizations</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify health-care organizations in your community that could potentially benefit from learning more about disability.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Organization Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Contact Person</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\