(118, 1, '2019-05-09 06:47:05', '2019-05-09 06:47:05', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Strengthen personal knowledge and skills</b></p>\r\n<p>Health information and education enables people with disabilities and their families to build the knowledge and life skills they need to maintain and improve their health. These include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>Disease risk factors</li>\r\n<li>Good hygiene</li>\r\n<li>Healthy eating choices</li>\r\n<li>The importance of physical activity and</li>\r\n<li>Other protective factors</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<h5><b>Identify existing health promotion resources</b></h5>\r\n<p>Identify existing health promotion resources that can help people with disabilities and their families acquire new knowledge and skills to remain healthy.</p>\r\n<b>Health promotion materials</b>\r\n<p>Identify and collect copies of existing health promotion materials to distribute to people with disabilities and their family members.</p>\r\n<p>When necessary, adapt these materials to make them accessible to people with disabilities, such as people with an intellectual disability will require materials that are simple and straightforward with basic language and relevant pictures.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Are materials accessible?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Local health promotion programmes and services</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify local health promotion programmes and services that people with disabilities can contact for additional information, training and support.</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Programme or Service Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>2. Connect people with disabilities with the health promotion resources they need</b></p>\r\n<p>Visit people with disabilities and their families in their homes, and identify their specific needs for health-related knowledge and skills. Then:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Distribute relevant health promotion materials\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Provide information about how to contact relevant health promotion programmes and services\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox113 class:checkbox \"Talk about how to maintain a healthy lifestyle, giving practical suggestions\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Assist people with disabilities and their families to engage assertively and confidently with health-care providers so they can ask questions and make decisions about their health\"]\r\n\r\n<p><b>3. Develop and provide additional customized training (as needed)</b></p>\r\n<p>Visit people with disabilities and their families in their homes, and identify their specific needs for health-related knowledge and skills. Then:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Develop specific education sessions, if necessary, for people with disabilities whose needs are not being met by those targeting the general community\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-720 id:checkbox112 class:checkbox \"Provide training for individuals with disabilities, in partnership with the health sector, to enable them to become health promotion educators \"]\r\n\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Strengthen personal knowledge and skills', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'encourage-immunization', '', '', '2019-05-09 12:58:19', '2019-05-09 12:58:19', '', 0, 'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=118', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(119, 1, '2019-05-09 06:47:05', '2019-05-09 06:47:05', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Encourage immunization</b></p>\r\n<p>Health information and education enables people with disabilities and their families to build the knowledge and life skills they need to maintain and improve their health. These include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>Disease risk factors</li>\r\n<li>Good hygiene</li>\r\n<li>Healthy eating choices</li>\r\n<li>The importance of physical activity and</li>\r\n<li>Other protective factors</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Identify existing immunization services</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify reputable services in your community where people with disabilities and their families can safely obtain immunizations.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Immunizations offered</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Is location accessible?</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Poliomyelitis\"]<br>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Diphtheria\"]<br>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Tetanus\"]<br>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Measles\"]<br>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"BCG (Tuberculosis)\"]<br>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\r\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</