(131, 1, '2019-05-10 06:07:11', '2019-05-10 06:07:11', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Facilitate access to maternal and child health care</b></p>\r\n<p>Ante-natal care, skilled care during delivery and post-natal care reduce the risk of mothers and babies developing health conditions and impairments that may lead to disability.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>Identify and support existing health-care services</b></p>\r\n<p>1. Identify <b>maternal health-care services</b>, such as ante-natal care, available in the communities that your organization serves:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-1 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-2 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-3 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-4 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-5 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-7 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-8 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-9 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-10 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-11 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-12 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-13 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-14 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-15 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact each of these services and provide advice on access issues faced by pregnant women with disabilities:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-667 id:cf-131-16 class:checkbox \"Provide suggestions about appropriate communication methods\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-667 id:cf-131-17 class:checkbox \"Provide advice on how to make hospitals and delivery rooms accessible\"]\r\n<p>2. Identify <b>genetic counseling services</b> available in the communities that your organization serves:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-18 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-19 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-20 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-21 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-22 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-23 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-24 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-25 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-26 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-27 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-28 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-29 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-30 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-31 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-32 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>3. Identify training programmes for traditional birth attendants in the communities you serve:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-32 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-33 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-34 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-35 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-36 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-37 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-38 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-39 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-40 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-41 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-42 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-43 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-44 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-45 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-46 class:text rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-130-22 class:checkbox \"Contact each of these training programmes and ensure that they include information on disability and the early recognition of impairments\"]\r\n<p><b>Support people with disabilities</b></p>\r\n<p>Provide women and their families with the following types of support:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-47 class:checkbox \"Provide all women with information about the maternal health services listed above, and encourage them to access these\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-48 class:checkbox \"Provide additional support for women with disabilities when access to maternal health-care services might be difficult\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><b>Example:</b> Provide advocacy where discrimination exists in the health-care system</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-49 class:checkbox \"Refer women and their families for genetic counselling when they have specific questions or concerns related to current or future pregnancies\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\"><b>Example:</b> A couple with a disabled child might ask if their next child will inherit the same condition/impairment.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">[checkbox checkbox-656 id:cf-131-50 class:checkbox \"Encourage families to register children with disabilities with the local authorities at birth so they can receive appropriate services\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--\r\n<p><b>Train CBR personnel</b></p>\r\n<p>Provide training to ensure that CBR personnel are able to perform the following tasks:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-52 \"Identify people with signs of malnutrition\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Screening should include all people (both with and without disabilities)</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2 \">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-53 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the health services identified above for proper assessment and management of cases of malnutrition\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-54 class:checkbox \"Provide referrals to the nutrition programmes listed above\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-55 \"Ensure that children with disabilities get sufficient and appropriate food to eat\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note:</b> Children with disabilities are often neglected, especially those with feeding problems</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-56 class:checkbox \"Ensure that children with disabilities are actively included in programmes that monitor growth and provide micronutrients and supplementary food\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-57 \"Identify people with disabilities who have feeding difficulties, and provide referrals to speech and language therapists where possible\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Children with cerebral palsy can have chewing and swallowing problems, as well as difficulty speaking</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical  p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-131-58 \"Encourage the use of iron-rich and vitamin-rich foods that are locally available\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Spinach, drumstick leaves, whole grains, papaya fruit</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-59 class:checkbox \"Demonstrate low-cost, nutritious recipes to encourage people to eat nutritious foods\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-131-60 class:checkbox \"Encourage pregnant women to attend ante-natal care for iron and folic acid supplements\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Facilitate access to maternal and child health care', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'untitled-12', '', '', '2019-05-10 09:23:07', '2019-05-10 09:23:07', '', 0, 'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=131', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
