(147, 1, '2019-05-13 10:26:18', '2019-05-13 10:26:18', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Ensure access to early treatment</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR can promote and encourage collaboration between people with disabilities, their families and primary health-care workers to increase access to medical-care services at all levels.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>To promote and encourage collaboration, CBR staff members should be able to perform the following tasks.</p>\r\n<p><b>Before, during and after medical appointments</b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Advocate for people with disabilities as needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><strong>Example:</strong> CBR personnel who know sign language may accompany deaf persons to health facilities to ensure that they are able to: <ul>\r\n<li>Communicate their needs</li>\r\n<li>Understand the information being provided</li>\r\n<li>Access appropriate treatment</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<p><b>After medical appointments</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Check with health workers to make sure individuals who have been included in screening activities are provided with follow-up medical care if needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox Check with health workers to make sure referrals have been made for individuals who require access to secondary and tertiary levels of health care]</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Ensure access to early treatment', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ensure-access-to-early-treatment-2', '', '', '2019-05-13 10:26:18', '2019-05-13 10:26:18', '', 0, 'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=147', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
