(161, 1, '2019-05-16 04:58:37', '2019-05-16 04:58:37', '<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Identify needs</b></h5>\r\n<p>Before making a rehabilitation plan and starting activities, CBR personnel need to carry out a basic assessment with an individual and his or her family members to identify needs and priorities. Assessment is an important skill, so CBR personnel should receive prior training and supervision to ensure competency in this area.</p>\r\n<p><em>This checklist spells out some of the most important tools CBR workers should use to collect the necessary information. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>A skilled assessment professional must be resourceful, collecting information through a variety of different means, including those listed below.</p>\r\n<p><b>Personal interviews and observation</b></p>\r\n<p>To identify a person’s rehabilitation needs, it is important to seek answers to the following questions, through observation or direct questioning of the individual, his or her family members and other members of the community who are familiar with the individual.</p>\r\n<p>1. What activities can this individual do and not do?</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Can do:</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Can\'t do</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-1 rows:3 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-2 rows:3 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>2. What does the individual want to be able to do?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-3 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>3. What problems do they experience? How and when did these problems begin?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>Problem</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\"><b>When and how did this problem begin?</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-4 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-5 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-6 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-7 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-8 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[textarea textarea-702 id:textarea class:cf-161-9 rows:2 cols:60]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>4. What areas are affected (e.g. body, senses, mind, communication, behavior)?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-10 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>5. What secondary problems are developing?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-11 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>6. What is their home and community situation like?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>7. In what way(s) have they adjusted to their disability?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n\r\n<p><b>Other sources of information</b></p>\r\n<p>In addition to observing and conducting discussions with the individual and his or her family members, useful information can also be obtained from the following sources:</p>\r\n<p>1. Review past medical records, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-12 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>2. Perform a basic physical examination of the individual, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-13 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p>3. Conduct discussions with involved health professionals/services, and note significant findings:</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-548 id:textarea class:cf-161-14 rows:3 cols:140]\r\n<p><b>Note</b>: It is important to keep a record of the initial assessment and future consultations, so an individual’s progress can be monitored over time.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is in